# BeVinci source hygiene policy.
#
# Do not apply a global text=auto rule yet.
# The imported Medo baseline contains a measured mixture of LF, CRLF, BOM,
# mixed line endings, and files without final newline.
#
# Existing source files must not be normalized accidentally as a side effect of
# unrelated functional changes. Any source normalization must happen in a
# separate, explicit hygiene commit.

*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.plugin text eol=lf
*.frag text eol=lf
*.vert text eol=lf
CMakeLists.txt text eol=lf
*.cmake text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.odt binary
*.pdf binary
*.ico binary
